 *General Housewares Corp., up 7 at 27 1/2    	
</P>
<P>
	Corning Consumer Products Co. will buy General Housewares Corp.  
for $28.75 a share cash, or $115 million total. General Housewares, 
based in Terre Haute, Ind., makes products for the housewares and 
craft-and-hardware markets. 

</P>
<P>
 *Horace Mann Educators Corp., up 4 3/4 at 29 15/16    	
</P>
<P>
	Horace Mann's board has hired Morgan Stanley Dean Witter &AMP; Co.  
and Credit Suisse First Boston to explore strategic alternatives. 
The company sells retirement annuities and automobile, homeowners 
and life insurance to educators. 

