</P>
<P>
	NeoPharm, a biopharmaceutical company, received an $8 million  
equity investment from Pharmacia &AMP; Upjohn Inc. NeoPharm said it 
sold 452,861 of its shares to Pharmacia &AMP; Upjohn for $17.67 a 
share. 



  	   	
