<HEADLINE>  Bills' Smith Loses Weight </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	FREDONIA, N.Y. (AP) -- When the Buffalo Bills opened camp over  
the weekend, one of the first things that caught their attention 
was a new and improved Antowain Smith. 
</P>
