</P>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- The threat of higher interest rates demolished a  
rally on Wall Street today: The Dow Jones industrial average ended 
down 9.19 at 10,645.96 after rising 136 points earlier in the 
session. On the NYSE, losers led gainers 1,762-1,225. The Nasdaq 
fell 14.86 to 2,623.63. 

