<HEADLINE> Dunston Joins Mets </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	MILWAUKEE (AP) -- Shawon Dunston, the last of four players  
acquired by the New York Mets just before the trading deadline, 
joined the club Monday. 
</P>
<P>
	Manager Bobby Valentine plans to use Dunston, who started 29 of  
his 62 games with St. Louis, off the bench. 
</P>
