<HEADLINE> `Will &AMP; Grace' Stars Get Porsches </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LOS ANGELES (AP) -- NBC decided to say ``thank you'' with  
Porsches. 
</P>
<P>
	The network gave the four lead actors on ``Will &AMP; Grace''  
matching silver Boxter sports cars for a job well done. The cars 
are worth $40,000 each. 
</P>
<P>
	Eric McCormack, Debra Messing, Sean Hayes and Megan Mullally  
were given keys to the cars Friday. 
</P>
<P>
	``It was a nice way for us to say thank you for a great first  
season,'' said Dave Bartus, an NBC vice president. ``We walked out 
into the parking lot and said, `There's one for each of you.' They 
seemed truly shocked.'' 
